tafsir[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,61,"Tuma nde Fir'awna e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen fewtundirnoo e Muusaa e yim…ìe mu'un, nokku ka wonnoo fedde kala no yi'ude ndeya, yim…ìe Muusaa …ìen wi'i: ""Pellet, Fir'awna e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen …ìe hewtitoto en, en alaa dartantoo…óo en …ìe""."
  26,62,"Muusaa maakani yim…ìe makko …ìen: ""Fiyaake …óen wanaa no miijorton non. Pellet, Joomi am no wonndiri e am semmbinngol e wallugol, O fewnay lam O tinndina lam faade e laawol da…óugol""."
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa ko Men yamiray …ìe mo yo o piyir maayo ngon tuggordu makko ndun, o piyiri ngo ndu, maayo ngon seekii ngo wonti boli sappoo e …ói…ói yeru limoore le∆¥∆¥i …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, kala huntere e ceeki maayo ngon foti e fello mawngo ka tii…óugol e ka tabitugol haa nokku ka ndiyam ilataa e majje."
  26,64,"Men …ìanni Firawna e yim…ìe makko …ìen haa …ìe naati ka maayo ko …ìe sikku…ìe wonnde laawol ngol ko lummbu ngol."
  26,65,"Men danndi Muusaa e …ìen wonndu…ìe e makko immorde e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, hay gooto e ma…ì…ìe halkanooka."
  26,66,"Refti Men halkiri Fir'awna e yim…ìe makko …ìen yooleede ka maayo."
  26,67,"Pellet, no e seekanagol maayo ngon Muusaa e da…óugol makko e halkeede Fir'awana e yim…ìe makko …ìen …óum ko Aaya tinndin…óo e dow goongugol Muusaa. ∆Åur…ìe heewude e …ìen wonndunoo…ìe e Fir'awna …ìe wonaano gom…óin…ìe."
  26,68,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo-ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ìtotoo…óo ay…ìe Makko …ìen, Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo e ma…ì…ìe."
  26,69,"Janngu e taweede ma…ì…ìe -an Nulaa…óo- fillayee fii Ibraahiima."
  26,70,"Tuma nde o wi'annoo baaba makko Aajara e yim…ìe mu'un …ìen: ""Ko hon…óum wonu…óon rewude gaanin Alla?"""
  26,71,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: ""Ko sanamuuji men rewata, men √±alla √±ii…ìude e rewugol …ói, ko men jokku…ìe …ói""."
  26,72,"Ibraahiima maakani …ìe: ""Yalli sanamuuji …óin no nana noddaandu mo'on ndun tuma noddoton …ói?"""
  26,73,"Kaa hi…ói nafa on si on …óoftike …ói, maa…óum …ói lorra on si on yeddii …ói?"
  26,74,"∆Åe wi'i: ""∆äi nanantaa men dey si men noddii …ói, …ói nafataa men kadi si men …óoftike …ói, …ói lorrataa men kadi si men yeddii…ói. Ko woni, tigi-tigi on, menen men tawiino baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen hi…ìe gollira nii, me…óen √±entinnde …ìe""."
  26,75,"Ibraahiima maaki: ""Enee, on taskike on yi'ii ko wonu…óon e rewude gaanin Alla immorde e sanamuuji …óin""."
  26,76,"Kon ko baabiraa…ìe moo…óon aran…ìe …ìen laatinoo no rewa."
  26,77,"Pellet, kam…ìe …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe ko …ìe ay…ìe am; sabu kam…ìe ko …ìe meere si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji …óin fow."
  26,78,"On Tagu…óo lam ko Kanko fewnata lam faade e mo∆¥∆¥ere aduna e Laakara."
  26,79,"On ko Kanko tun √±amminta lam si mi weelaama, O yarna lam si mi …óon…óaama."
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii ko Kanko tun woni sellinay…óo lam immorde e nawnaare nden, mi alaa sellinoowo ngoo tanaa makko."
  26,81,"E On taw…óo ko Kanko tun warata lam si lajal am ngal timmii, O wurnita lam kadi …ìaawo mayde am nden."
  26,82,"Ko Kanko tun mi jortii yawtanay lam goopi am …óin √ëalnde njo…ìdi ndin."
  26,83,"Ibraahiima noddi Joomi makko o maaki: Joomam okkam faamugol Diina kan, wattidaa mi e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen immorde e Annabaa…ìe adii…ìe lam …ìen, …óum woni naadaa mi ka Aljanna wonndude e ma…ì…ìe""."
